Package: SEMseeker
Type: Package
Title: Stochastic Epigenetic Mutations SEM Seeker
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luigi", "Corsaro",
        email = "lcorsaro69@gmail.com",
        role  = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1218-230X")),
    person("Centro Diagnostico Italiano S.p.A. - Genetic Medical Laboratory - Milan - Italy",
        role = "fnd"))
Description: Detection, quantification and association analysis of Stochastic
    Epigenetic Mutations (SEMs) from Illumina DNA methylation array data
    (EPIC 850k, 450k, 27k). Computes binary SEM calls and continuous deviation
    metrics (DeltaR, DeltaRP, DeltaRQ), aggregates mutations into genomic
    lesions, and provides downstream association analysis and pathway
    enrichment via multiple backends (WebGestalt, STRINGdb, pathfindR, CTD).
